{"tid":1432192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到人人睇到］警狗有最新玩法　被捕後入狗屋須知 （咪以為自己識，全部同我入黎睇曬佢！）","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:25:30.000Z","uid":172979,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"beb86b8ee1759e7dad7980a839b84e07389dd02c","tid":1432192,"uid":172979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"最近有義務大狀同返我講，佢地呢排係狗屋成日見到有義士同POPO講拒絕見律師<br />\n<br />\n事後果位大狀千辛萬苦見到果位義士，聽佢講返原來POPO同佢講：<br />\n<br />\n黑警說：「而家同你落口供，拿，一陣你咩都唔講就得，唔洗叫律師架喇，佢黎到都係叫你唔好講嘢既姐，你叫律師仲等得耐」<br />\n<br />\n黑警又講：「同埋，你叫律師入黎，分分鐘之後收你錢呀」<br />\n<br />\n最後，真係有義士拒絕見律師&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n咁做既後果係咩？無人提早幫你「預備」搜屋，幾時被人帶上庭無人知，孤立無援！<br />\n<br />\n重申入到狗屋你「唔好思考」就照做既事：<br />\n<br />\n-無論任何情況都係「我唔會回應任何問題」<br />\n-一定要！要求律師陪同先落文 (DLLM而家係唔係都扣留你48，你早啲落完文唔會早走到)<br />\n-什麼文件都唔簽（有權唔簽口供紙）<br />\n-拒絕自己寫或攝錄口供<br />\n<br />\n推到人人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf362bc232626f627656e04e5d75d2244f8c9f09","tid":1432192,"uid":198348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff397b9f57133363af5dcc052efc8368962d05d0","tid":1432192,"uid":172979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38afd24dc48232429f9696921f5228fad2a0bd3e","tid":1432192,"uid":131404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"醒喇大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要搵律師呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec532229ee178a43c008ee50e135514bf35f60f","tid":1432192,"uid":211958,"like":0,"disl